graph LR
    TrainingOp[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>Version: 1.9.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+<br/>REQUIRED]
    TrainingOp -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>OPTIONAL]
