    TrainingOp -.->|traffic mgmt| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Sidecar injection disabled]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
